nt-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">口ボーナス(*1)」の真っ只中です。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　総人口の</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">平均</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年齢</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">は</span>2012<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年時点で</span>28.2<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">！日本の</span>45.4<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">に比べ、約</span>17<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳も若いの</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">で</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">す。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">この人口</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ボーナス、</span>2040<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年ごろまで続く見込みとのこと。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ベトナムの「人」の良さはその若さだけではあり</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ません。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">日本人と近い気質や親日的である点、勤勉さもまた彼らの魅力です。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　最初はシャイなところがあるベトナム人ですが、親しくなっていくうちに様々な場所に連れて行ってくれたり、<br />風邪をひいたといえば自ら薬を買って来てくれたり･･･。<br />「助け合うことが当たり前」というベトナム人の精神は「義理人情」に似たも</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">のを感じます。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">いつも笑顔で手を差し伸べてくれる彼らが困っていれば、もちろんこちらも助けずにはいられません。<br />そんな</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">相互作用が</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">私達の関係をより</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">良いものにしてくれます。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　仕事に対して</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">も真面目で、依頼に一生懸命に応えようと取り組んでくれるベトナムの人材たち。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fa