</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">皆さんこんにちは！ここではベトナムの「人」の魅力についてお伝えしま</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">す。</span><br /> 　2013<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年末に</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">人</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">口が</span>9000<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">万人を超え、その約</span>70<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">％が生産年齢人口</span>(15<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">～</span>64<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳</span>)<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">であるベト</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ナム</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">まさに今、「人</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">口ボーナス(*1)」の真っ只中です。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　総人口の</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">平均</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年齢</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">は</span>2012<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年時点で</span>28.2<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">！日本の</span>45.4<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">に比べ、約</span>17<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">歳も若いの</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">で</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">す。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">この人口</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ボーナス、</span>2040<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年ごろまで続く見込みとのこと。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ベトナムの「人」の良さはその若さだけではあり</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ません。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">日本人と近い気質や親日的である点、勤勉さもまた彼らの魅力です。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　最初はシャイなところがあるベトナム人ですが、親しくなっていくうちに様々な場所に連れて行ってくれたり、<br />風邪をひいたといえば自ら薬を買って来てくれたり･･･。<br />「助け合うことが当たり前」というベトナム人の精神は「義理人情」に似たも</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">のを感じます。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">いつも笑顔で手を差し伸べてくれる彼らが困っていれば、もちろんこちらも助けずにはいられません。<br />そんな</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">相互作用が</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">私達の関係をより</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">良いものにしてくれます。</span><br /> <span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　仕事に対して</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">も真面目で、依頼に一生懸命に応えようと取り組んでくれるベトナムの人材たち。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ときには寝る間を惜しんで期待以上の成果を見せてくれることも。<br />また、新しいスキルや知識を得ることにも貪欲で、終業後に専門学校に通う姿も多く見かけます。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　毎年</span>5<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">％以上の経済成長率</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">を見せ、今後更なる成長が見込まれるベトナム。<br />そんなベトナムを支えていく、若くて活気あふれる「人」。</span><br /><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">温かく</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">、</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">そ</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"fo