o-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　　　　　　</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">　　　</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">新し</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'ＭＳ 明朝\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">いビジネスに回すことができる。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n', '魅力溢れるベトナムの「人」', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '84-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-01-28 18:56:41', '2014-01-28 09:56:41', '', 84, 'http://evacorp.localhost/wp/%e6%9c%aa%e5%88%86%e9%a1%9e/84-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
